I was planning to submit this story to Chalange, but they limit 
adventures to 4000 words.  When my rough draft hit 1200 - and I was only 
a fourth of the way through - I decided to develop my \'other\' story 
idea for Challange. (which I havent even started yet)

And what about my old story?  Well, I\'m submitting the portion I saved to 
disk.  If you like, I\'ll submit the rest within the week.  If not... 
well, at least I didn\'t submit this to Challange.
