over 1 million, with the old Vume culture forgotten by all but the 
museums.  Seeing how Regency Nobility was losing power, Alco\'s elders 
made him join the Regency Electorial Office, to get a firsthand feel of 
the New Democracy - and see how the Vume families can cut a niche in it.

