grant\'s her the stamina to endure any trial: however, her spritual 
orientation(ie. her lips moving in silent prayer, unexpected religious 
trances, religious laguage popping into non-religious conversation, 
talking to angels) can make people nervous.  However, her natural love of 
people - especially the poor, sickly and hurting - tend to cover her 
faults.  She still has some very weird eating habits, though.

Her most enjoyable pastime isher soaring chant\'s: she\'s always learning 
new chant\'s to add to her extensive repritore.  When attacked, she 
react\'s in a passive-aggresive manner, often infuriating her opponenbt or 
dumping guilt on them.  Her most deadly weapon is a low-profile, 
razor-sharp wit: she can make even the most arrogant and proud 
opponentlook like a blind and stupid fool, but she\'ll never openly and 
directly attack anyone.

Usually quite easygoing, she can be stubborn and manipulative over issues 
she feels is important.  Oftentimes, she can even literally get sick 
until she get\'s what she want\'s.

