enrolled in the Society of Mary Magalene.  She enjoyed her stay at the 
convent at Ash, and now- after an extensive education, Adept Forentine - 
and her Champion, Aleksandr Suvarov - is preparing to enter the Wilds, to 
recontact the faithful of the Imperial Church, convert the heathen, 
spread antiviral tools and techniques, and gather sociological 
information to bring back to the Church leaders on Mora.

Ambition: Leonidas hopes to do a good enough job so that not only will 
she be initated into full sisterhood, but be given a pernament mission to
tend.

