    'body' => '"David A. Nelson" <34TYHPE@CMUVM.CSV.CMICH.EDU> writes:

>I would like to see the other aslan careers, as I found that article 
>quite useful. Also, has anyone tried doing Vargr, Droyne, Zhodani, or 
